definition: to cross/to go over/to pass (time)/to celebrate (a holiday)/to live/to get along/excessively/too-

sentences.english: Fashion takes itself way too seriously and has a sense of exclusivity.
sentences.chinese: 時尚界自視過高，具有一種排他感。

sentences.english: I do think the current education fee is too high for some poor students.
sentences.chinese: 我確實覺得現在的教育費用對一些貧困生來說過高了。

sentences.english: First, I remind myself of the phenomenon of unconscious over-claiming;
sentences.chinese: 第一，我提醒自己當心下意識的要求過高現象。

sentences.english: As one of the most used tool to fight against corruption, the cost of monitoring is too high.
sentences.chinese: 打擊腐敗固然能懲前毖後，但成本過高。

sentences.english: If the grass is too tall, mowing in two stages is recommended.
sentences.chinese: 如果草長得過高，建議你分兩個階段刈草。

sentences.english: But, if blood is calcic content is exorbitant, can hamper zincic absorption.
sentences.chinese: 但是，如果血鈣含量過高，則會妨礙鋅的吸收。

sentences.english: The price would be high as the witch was famous for the exorbitant prices she charged.
sentences.chinese: 但是，代價會很高，老巫婆正是因爲要價過高而出名。

sentences.english: When the alloy contains no or excess magnesium, its creep properties will decline.
sentences.chinese: 不含鎂或鎂含量過高的合金，其蠕變性能均有所下降。

sentences.english: It was not good for protoplast isolation at too high or low concentration of cellulase.
sentences.chinese: 纖維素酶濃度過高或過低均使產量和活力降低。

sentences.english: I still think the CD-player I bought from them was a rip off.
sentences.chinese: 我仍然認爲我從他們那兒買的CD機要價過高。

sentences.english: U.S. acting Deputy Secretary of Energy Jeffrey Kupfer said oil prices are clearly too high.
sentences.chinese: 美國能源部代理副部長庫普福說，石油價格顯然過高。

sentences.english: The cost of today's micro-irrigation systems, however, is still high.
sentences.chinese: 但目前的微灌系統成本仍然過高。

sentences.english: It's better if expectations are not too high.
sentences.chinese: 人們最好不要期待值過高。

sentences.english: where you don't have any sort of expectations that you have to worry about from others.
sentences.chinese: 你無需擔心別人對你抱有過高的期待。

sentences.english: Fruit is medium sized elongated conically shaped with very smooth skin and a high sugar content.
sentences.chinese: 果實中型細長錐形非常光滑皮膚和糖分過高。

sentences.english: Do not expect too much of him.
